가격대비 훌륭해요
근데
초록색 살껄 그랬어요 ㅎㅎㅎㅎㅎ
공부용으로는 딱인데, 식탁에 놓고 쓰시려면 키높이 방석 사셔야할거예요 ㅎㅎ 그래도 등받이가 편하고 소리도 안나고 좋아요

Color: The color looks elegant. Grey is a safe color! I love it!

Size: I thought it would be smaller but it is actually enough. I am 164cm but I can sit comfortably on it for hours.

Quality: It's very sturdy, comfortable and the price is not expensive compared to other chairs online.

Plus: You can even fold it and put it in some corner especially if your place is small.
